name: My Window #7
description:
Ana, she is my girl and she makes me feel like nobody does. 
By his side, I feel wonderful. If somebody asks me how I feel last year I will ask loved. She is a really great artist and motivates me to grow up in art and as a human.
I´m better because of her love.
She comes to my home, I didn´t doubt about taking a picture of her in front of my window.
Thanks, Annette, I love you.
Here you are, till blockchain expires, immortalized.
